'''Ichud''' ((אִחוּד) '''’ichūdh''', '''ihud''') [[Hebrew language|Hebrew]] word meaning "union". Also:

*Modern Hebrew word for [[Union]]
*Modern Hebrew word for [[Union (set theory)]]
*''Ha'ichud Ha'Leumi'', [[National Union]] political party in [[Israel]]
*Cultural (Spiritual, Religious) [[Zionist]] group, phisophy in the Palestine, like [[Martin Buber]], [[Hugo Bergman]]

